Summary: Utilities for roc-toolkit
Requires: %{name}%{?_isa} = %{version}-%{release}
 
%description utils
Utilities for roc-toolkit.
 
%package doc
Summary: Documentation for roc-toolkit
 
%description doc
Documentation for roc-toolkit.
 
